'''Hyber Canyon''' was located on [[Jabiim/Legends|Jabiim]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], it was the site of the [[Jabiimi Nationalists|Jabiimi Nationalist]] command center, and was a [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]] staging area. It was [[Battle of Hyber Canyon|attacked]] by the [[Jabiimi Loyalists]].<ref name="Empire 32">[[Empire 32|''Empire'' 32]]</ref>

